                        </div>
                    </div>
                </li>

                <li>
                    <div class="reveal_steps1 ctnr">
                        <div class="icon_ctnr">
                            <div class="gradient_cone"></div>
                            <Scale/>
                        </div>

                        <div class="content">
                            <h4>3. Scale with Ease</h4>
                            
                            <p>With streamlined processes and insights, grow your business confidently and efficiently.</p>
                        </div>
